Package: sangr
Title: Simulate Sanger Sequencing Chromatograms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Simon",
           family = "Andrews",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "simon.andrews@babraham.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5006-3507"))
Description: Generates either per base density data for simulated sanger sequences, or produces actual chromatogram line graphs. It can add noise, dye blobs, and simulate degradation over time. Allows for either clean or mixed sequence traces.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
